		Elastic Load Balancers Exam Tips


2 types of Load Balancers
- Application Load Balancer
- Classic Load Balancer

Application Load Balancer
- work at layer 7
- the preferred load balancer for http/https

Classic Load Balancer
- layer 4 load balancer

Unheatlhy threshold: how many times of failure before being classified as unhealthy

Don't use public IP addresses for ELB. Use DNS names.

Once your EC2 instance is out of service the ELB will not send traffic to that EC2 instance because its failing the health check

1 subnet = 1 availability zone

Instances monitored by ELB are reported as: 
- InService
- OutofService

Health Checks check the instance health by talking to it

ELBs have their own DNS name. You are never given an IP address

Read the ELB FAQ for Classic Load Balancers

